'''Alɣem''' neɣ '''Alɣem aserɣin''' ([[Assaɣ usnan]]: ''Camelus dromedarius'') d [[tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] n [[aɣersiw|iɣersiwen]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[Tileɣmatin|tleɣmatin]] deg [[Tafesna|tfesna]] n [[Tisenfednin|tsenfednin]], Ar tura ur yittwassen uẓar neɣ tamurt taẓaṛant n welɣem maca llan imusnawen id yeqqaren d akken-it yekka-d seg [[Tazunegzirt taɛrabt|tzunegzirt taserɣint]]

Ass-a, [[Talmest|Tilmas]] [[agrad|timegrudin]] ttidirent deg [[Asamar alemmas|usamar alemmas]] d [[Tafriqt n ugafa|Tefrikt ugafa]] d [[Lhend|ugafa n Lhend]] 

Alɣem d aɣersiw yettusexdem s waṭas i yinig deg [[Taneẓruft|tniri]] ɣef anect-a llan wid is yessemman '''Aɣerrabu n tinri'''

